Rules

 

"{s} is deleted following a consonant"
%{s%}:0 <=> :Cons %>: _ ;

"{E} becomes y when following a vowel"
%{E%}:a <=> :Cons %>: _ ;

"{K} becomes g when it is before a vowel"
%{K%}:g <=>  _ %>: (:0) :Vow ;

"{Q} becomes gʻ when it is before a vowel"
%{q%}:gʻ <=>  _ %>: (:0) :Vow ;

"{i} becomes i when following a consonant"
%{i%}:0 <=> :Vow %>: _ ;


